<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 06:14:42 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国的增长模式使北京陷入更多贸易冲突</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-growth-model-pushes-beijing-into-more-trade-conflicts-2024-01-29/</link><description>瑞士太阳能电池板制造商梅耶博格正面临来自中国的竞争，并警告称，除非政府介入提供财政支持，否则该公司可能不得不关闭其在德国亏损的生产工厂。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 06:05:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-growth-model-pushes-beijing-into-more-trade-conflicts-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，台湾第四季度经济增长因内需和出口反弹而​​回升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-q4-economic-growth-seen-picking-up-domestic-demand-export-rebound-2024-01-29/</link><description>路透周一的一项民意调查显示，由于国内消费强劲和出口反弹，台湾依赖贸易的经济第四季度的增长可能快于第三季度。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 06:04:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-q4-economic-growth-seen-picking-up-domestic-demand-export-rebound-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾马科斯表示海上合作是越南访问的基石</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-marcos-says-maritime-cooperation-cornerstones-vietnam-visit-2024-01-29/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周一表示，菲律宾与越南之间的海上合作会谈将成为与东南亚邻国建立战略伙伴关系的基石之一。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 04:54:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-marcos-says-maritime-cooperation-cornerstones-vietnam-visit-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>反应：中国恒大被香港法院下令清算</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-evergrande-ordered-liquidate-by-hong-kong-court-2024-01-29/</link><description>香港一家法院周一下令对中国恒大集团进行清算，此举可能会在中国摇摇欲坠的金融市场中引发连锁反应，因为政策制定者正忙于遏制日益加深的危机。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 03:55:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-evergrande-ordered-liquidate-by-hong-kong-court-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>解说：恒大被勒令清算后接下来会发生什么？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/what-happens-next-after-china-evergrande-ordered-liquidate-2024-01-29/</link><description>香港一家法院周一下令对全球负债最重的开发商中国恒大进行清算。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 02:47:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/what-happens-next-after-china-evergrande-ordered-liquidate-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>时间表：恒大危机恶化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/worsening-crisis-evergrande-worlds-most-indebted-developer-2024-01-29/</link><description>香港法院周一下令对中国恒大集团进行清算。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 02:40:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/worsening-crisis-evergrande-worlds-most-indebted-developer-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>反应：香港法院下令中国恒大清算</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/view-china-evergrande-ordered-liquidate-by-hong-kong-court-2024-01-29/</link><description>香港一家法院周一下令对中国恒大集团进行清算，此举可能会在中国摇摇欲坠的金融市场中引发连锁反应，因为政策制定者正忙于遏制日益加深的危机。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 02:36:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/view-china-evergrande-ordered-liquidate-by-hong-kong-court-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯军舰在南海进行反潜演习--机构</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-warship-conducts-anti-submarine-drill-south-china-sea-agencies-2024-01-29/</link><description>俄罗斯通讯社周一援引俄罗斯太平洋舰队新闻部门的消息称，俄罗斯太平洋舰队“沙波什尼科夫元帅”号护卫舰已在南海进行了反潜演习。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 02:23:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-warship-conducts-anti-submarine-drill-south-china-sea-agencies-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国推动亚洲股市上涨，红海担忧导致油价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-29/</link><description>监管机构周末采取新措施支持市场后，中国股市本周开始领涨亚洲股市。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 02:22:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国医疗器械公司迈瑞计划以9.27亿美元收购亚太医疗</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinese-medical-device-firm-mindray-plans-927-mln-deal-control-apt-medical-2024-01-29/</link><description>中国医疗器械公司深圳迈瑞生物医疗电子表示，计划以 66.5 亿元人民币（9.27 亿美元）的交易获得 APT Medical 的控制权，以扩大心血管疾病相关业务。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 01:58:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinese-medical-device-firm-mindray-plans-927-mln-deal-control-apt-medical-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>投资者关注美联储周繁忙数据，美元持稳</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-cautious-start-busy-data-fed-week-2024-01-29/</link><description>美元本周开局稳定，因投资者在本周美联储政策会议之前评估美国经济数据，而中东地缘政治紧张局势升级抑制了风险情绪。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 01:46:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-cautious-start-busy-data-fed-week-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>与顶级债权人谈判破裂后恒大面临迫在眉睫的清算 - 华尔街日报</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/evergrande-faces-imminent-liquidation-after-talks-with-top-creditors-break-down-2024-01-29/</link><description>据《华尔街日报》周日援引知情人士的话报道，中国房地产开发商恒大地产面临迫在眉睫的清算，因为其海外债权人未能在本周末的第 11 小时内就重组这家规模庞大的房地产公司达成重组协议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 01:29:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/evergrande-faces-imminent-liquidation-after-talks-with-top-creditors-break-down-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国将把三大资产管理公司并入中国投资有限责任公司-新华社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-merge-three-major-asset-managers-into-china-investment-corp-xinhua-2024-01-29/</link><description>据官方媒体新华社财经报道，作为金融机构改革计划的一部分，中国计划将国内三大坏账管理公司并入主权财富基金中国投资有限责任公司（CIC）（CIC.UL）。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 01:27:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-merge-three-major-asset-managers-into-china-investment-corp-xinhua-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>香港法院命令中国恒大清算3000亿美元债务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/embattled-china-evergrande-back-court-liquidation-hearing-2024-01-28/</link><description>香港一家法院周一下令对房地产巨头中国恒大集团进行清算，此举可能会在中国摇摇欲坠的金融市场中引发连锁反应，因为政策制定者正忙于遏制日益加深的危机。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 23:15:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/embattled-china-evergrande-back-court-liquidation-hearing-2024-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国 PMI 和美联储决定将带来更多欢呼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-01-28/</link><description>美联储的行动和主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔的新闻发布会将主导会议进程。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 21:49:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-01-28/</guid></item></channel></rss>